nhc_headline: ...PILAR MOVING QUICKLY WESTWARD OVER OPEN WATERS...
summary:
...PILAR MOVING QUICKLY WESTWARD OVER OPEN WATERS...
 As of 3:00 AM MDT Sat Nov 4
 the center of Pilar was located near 9.8, -107.3
 with movement W at 16 mph.
 The minimum central pressure was 1002 mb
 with maximum sustained winds of about 45 mph.
